    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, characterized by its eight individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is robust, featuring a precise 6-speed manual transmission paired with a functional M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral dynamics. Recent preventative maintenance includes a critical rod bearing replacement and new throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the high-pressure VANOS system. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback expected from this chassis. While the finish shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the powertrain and subframe integrity make this a turn-key performance machine for the serious driver.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
