    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available now is a meticulously cared-for 2017 Porsche Macan S finished in a sophisticated Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle has served as a reliable and spirited daily driver, showing the pride of ownership through its comprehensive service history. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel rim\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior remains supple and clean; the bolsters show minimal wear, and the cabin has never been smoked in. All technological features, including the premium Bose surround sound system, navigation, and heated seating, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. I have maintained a complete file of service records, including the most recent 60,000-mile interval service which included a fresh oil change, new spark plugs, and a brake fluid flush. The Michelin Latitude tires have plenty of life left with roughly 7/32\" tread depth. This Macan S offers a perfect balance of utility and performance, driving as tightly as the day it left the showroom. Sold with two keys and a clean title.",
      "price": 35800.0,
